title: Being Jimmy Fallon
description:
A nervous man asks his girlfriends father the big question.

Written by Jasmine Pierce
Featuring Michael Delisle, Tristan Griffin, Maya Deshmukh and Willy Appelman
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
